#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:57
msgid ""
"`RipPhase1Process.bpmn` — the executable process. ServiceTasks use "
"`camunda:type=\"external\"` with topics `rip-edocs-workspace` and `rip-edocs-"
"document`, polled by the LDE backend external task worker."
