#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:94
msgid ""
"Open `RipPhase1Process.bpmn` in the BPMN Modeler and click **Deploy**. The "
"modal resolves all `camunda:formRef` and `ronl:documentRef` attributes "
"automatically and lists all 12 resources. Click **Deploy to Operaton** to "
"deploy."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:96
msgid ""
"!!! tip Set a Business Key equal to the project number when starting the "
"process from the Operaton Cockpit. This makes process instances easy to find "
"by project number."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:101
msgid "Starting the process"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:103
msgid ""
"The process is designed to be started from the Human Tasks interface in "
"MijnOmgeving (or the Operaton Tasklist), not directly from the Cockpit. "
"Starting from the Cockpit's generic start dialog is possible for testing — "
"click **Start** and the first user task (`Complete intake form`) will appear "
"in the task list immediately."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:105
msgid ""
"!!! note `candidateGroups` is set to `infra-projectteam` for all tasks by "
"the DMN. Any user with this group membership can claim tasks."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:110
msgid "eDOCS integration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:112
msgid ""
"The three ServiceTasks in the process write documents to the project "
"workspace in eDOCS. In stub mode (`EDOCS_STUB_MODE=true`), the external task "
"worker returns realistic fake responses and logs all calls. No code changes "
"are needed when switching to a live eDOCS server — set "
"`EDOCS_STUB_MODE=false` and provide the real credentials."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Crip-phase1-bundle.md:114
msgid "See [eDOCS Integration]{1} for setup and configuration."
msgstr ""
